item.title: 400 entries!
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: According to my Movable Type admin tool, that last entry was entry 400 for me. 400 entries ranging from simple comments, the occasional rambling essay, reblogs, whoring, to (most recently) movie quotes. So in honor of this momentous occasion, all of you... Shake your ass! Whoo!
